<div class="nbunit" id="3Jun1936"><font color="red">3 June 1936</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to T.S. Eliot) L&eacute;on will undertake the work of course but he says it is not the same thing now as it would have been in January when the text, with insertions and alignments, was quite fresh in his mind. </div>
